</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='monitored_conditions' href='#monitored_conditions'></a> monitored_conditions</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='list'>list</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>A list of sensor to include.</p>
</span></p></dd><dd><dl class='nested'><dt><a class='title-link' name='collection' href='#collection'></a> collection</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='description'><p>Shows the amount of records in the userâ€™s collection.</p>
</span></p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='wantlist' href='#wantlist'></a> wantlist</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='description'><p>Shows the amount of records in the userâ€™s wantlist.</p>
